rComments: Reading material is usually very interesting. However, can get rather repetitive. Pat Gill's lectures are worthless and incomprehensible. Think twice before taking a course with her.
Pat is amazing.  I learned more from her personal stories than anything else.  She is so hilarious and easy-going.

Pat Gill is great. I actually look forward to her lectures.  She is an extremely interesting person, and very funny in a crude way but that is my humor so it works. She doesn't use profanity in a "I'm trying to be hip and appeal to these young kids" kind of way, it's just how she is which is good and makes it not annoying.
Such an interesting prof and class.  Sure, she tells wild stories and makes crazy jokes, but she also shows that she's human and affected by the same things we are.

Pat Gill is hilarious! I love her class and she has such an interesting and engaging personality and the material and class is never boring. She's the kind of professor that you'd want to go to her office hours just to talk to her one on one because she's so interesting and engaging.

Wow, talk about a couple of prude (the reviewers before me). Sure Pat uses foul language and tells crazy stories, but I find it refreshing. I think what the other reviewers missed entirely is her knowledge of the material covered. I really enjoyed her lectures, and I definitely recommend her.
Pat is one of my favorite professor's. Her lectures are almost always interesting (and funny), and she had a very commanding knowledge of the topic and readings.

She uses incredibly foul language and talks about past drug use and things of that nature... as a means of impressing students, I guess.  She's tacky and she rambles constantly.  It's an interesting class, but she demands attendance which is really annoying.  The TA is what made this a good class.

Professor Gill is TERRIBLE!!!  She thinks for some reason that she is a comedian and that is her new profession when she is teaching.  She uses words that my physics professor wouldn't understand.  She also tends to use foul language which makes her even more less attractive, which I thought was impossible.  DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS WITH HER!!!
She was an amazing Prf.  take any of her classes you will learn more about real life that you will actually use.
Very interesting professor with MANY stories about her life and her experiences.
Fun, fascinating, experienced and knowlegible. I wish I could take this class again.

One of my favorite professors at this school. Her stories were humorous and usually relevant to the topics. She's extremely bright and very personable. More professors should learn to be like Pat Gill.
Really funny. One of the best story tellers in the world and all relates to what you're supposed to learn in a crazy way. Take her class if you want fun but you can do work. Hard grader.
Entertaining lecturer, easy class, really interesting content, I'd definitely take another one of her classes
Hella smart and very funny - MENSA hotness!
